OL,3,CAir traffic control engineers working
OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FA review of the August bank holiday
OL,8,Fair traffic control (ATC) meltdown has
OL,9,Fhighlighted a "significant lack of pre-
OL,10,Fplanning" and engineers being allowed
OL,11,Fto work from home.
OL,13,FNearly 750,000 passengers were
OL,14,Fdisrupted when flights were grounded
OL,15,Fat UK airports on August 28 last year.
OL,17,FATC provider National Air Traffic
OL,18,FServices (Nats) suffered a technical
OL,19,Fglitch while processing a flight plan.
