OL,3,CAir traffic control engineers working
OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAn interim report from an inquiry
OL,8,Ffound there does not appear to have
OL,9,Fbeen "any multi-agency rehearsal of
OL,10,Fthe management of an incident of this
OL,11,Fnature and scale".
OL,13,FSuch rehearsals are "regularly
OL,14,Fconducted in other sectors", the
OL,15,Finquiry panel said.
