OL,3,CAir traffic control engineers working
OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe interim report, published by
OL,8,Fregulator the Civil Aviation Authority
OL,9,F(CAA), went on: "It is clear there is
OL,10,Fa significant lack of pre-planning and
OL,11,Fco-ordination for major events and
OL,12,Fincidents that targets the alleviation
OL,13,Fand remediation of major incidents."
