OL,3,CAir traffic control engineers working
OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe inquiry found that Nats' rostering
OL,8,Fof engineers is based "primarily" on
OL,9,Fthe amount of work planned, so on
OL,10,Fpublic holidays ` when maintenance is
OL,11,Fnot routinely scheduled ` it is
OL,12,F"common practice for staff to be
OL,13,Favailable on standby at remote
OL,14,Flocations ` typically at home".
OL,16,FOn the day of the ATC failure, it took
OL,17,F90 minutes for the Level 2 on-call
OL,18,Fengineer to "arrive on-site in order
OL,19,Fto perform the necessary full system
OL,20,Frestart which was not permitted
OL,21,Fremotely", the report said.
