OL,3,CAir traffic control engineers working
OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe assistance of a more senior
OL,8,Fengineer was not sought "for more than
OL,9,Fthree hours after the initial
OL,10,Ffailure", it added.
OL,12,FTim Alderslade, chief executive of
OL,13,FAirlines UK, the industry body
OL,14,Frepresenting UK-registered carriers,
OL,15,Fsaid: "This report contains damning
OL,16,Fevidence that Nats' basic resilience
OL,17,Fplanning and procedures were wholly
OL,18,Finadequate and fell well below the
OL,19,Fstandard that should be expected for
OL,20,Fnational infrastructure of this
OL,21,Fimportance.
