OL,3,CAir traffic control engineers working
OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"We welcome the committee's plans for
OL,8,Ffurther investigation to provide
OL,9,Frecommendations so that this kind of
OL,10,Fcatastrophic failure is not allowed to
OL,11,Fhappen again."
OL,13,FNats said in a statement on August 28
OL,14,Fit followed "engineering protocols"
OL,15,Fand there were "engineers both on site
OL,16,Fand on call".
OL,18,FIt added: "The Level 2 on-call
OL,19,Fengineers are individual system
OL,20,Fexperts and able to start working
OL,21,Fimmediately when issues arise.
