OL,3,CAir traffic control engineers working
OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"They were not able to fix the issue
OL,8,Fremotely in this case."
OL,10,FThe review found that Nats' flight
OL,11,Fplan processing system received a plan
OL,12,Fwith two waypoints ` which represent
OL,13,Fparticular locations ` that had the
OL,14,Fsame abbreviations.
OL,16,FThe system generated a "critical
OL,17,Fexception error" and shut down to
OL,18,F"prevent the transfer of apparently
OL,19,Fcorrupt flight data to the air traffic
OL,20,Fcontrollers", the report said.
