OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe panel described the financial cost
OL,8,Fto passengers as "very considerable",
OL,9,Fbut noted that the "stress and
OL,10,Fanxiety" was "at least as serious".
OL,12,FSome travellers were stranded overseas
OL,13,Ffor several days because of the number
OL,14,Fof flight cancellations.
