OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe combined cost to airlines in
OL,8,Fproviding refunds, rebookings, hotel
OL,9,Frooms and refreshments to affected
OL,10,Fpassengers was previously estimated at
OL,11,Faround #100 million by industry body
OL,12,Fthe International Air Transport
OL,13,FAssociation (Iata).
OL,15,FSeveral airlines including Ryanair
OL,16,Fhave called for Nats to be liable for
OL,17,Fthe cost of disruption it causes.
