OL,3,CAir traffic control engineers working
OL,4,Cfrom home during meltdown - report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe review panel said it has
OL,8,F"concerns" that Nats' performance is
OL,9,Fmeasured in delay minutes but does not
OL,10,Ftake account for the impact of
OL,11,Fcancellations and knock-on delays.
OL,13,FThe report said: "It appears
OL,14,Finappropriate that (Nats) is likely to
OL,15,Fachieve almost all of its performance
OL,16,Ftargets in 2023, and to suffer very
OL,17,Flittle financial consequence, after
OL,18,Fhaving caused such huge and serious
OL,19,Fdisruption to passengers, as well as
OL,20,Fconsiderable costs for airlines,
OL,21,Fairports and tour operators."
