OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe inquiry was set up by the CAA and
OL,8,Fis being led by Jeff Halliwell, who
OL,9,Fhas served as a chief executive and
OL,10,Fnon-executive director in roles across
OL,11,Fthe private and public sector.
OL,13,FA spokesman for Nats said it "co-
OL,14,Foperated fully" with the review and
OL,15,Fwill "continue to respond
OL,16,Fconstructively to any further requests
OL,17,Fto support the panel's ongoing work".
